  "name": "Stance: Arcane Cascade: Invigorate",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> <span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">You reduce a creature to 0 Hit Points with Spell or Spellstrike.</span></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wielding your black blade.</p><hr /><p>Your black blade becomes invigorated and your melee Strikes with it deal 1 additional damage for 1 minute. This additional damage increases to 2 if you have weapon specialization and 3 if you have greater weapon specialization. This damage is of the same type as the Arcane Cascade stance. Strikes that benefit from this damage gain the arcane trait, making them magical.</p><p>If your black blade uses this ability on a creature below your level, you must attempt a Will save against its Ego.</p><p>Despite being a minion, your black blade gains 1 reaction at the start of its turns, which it can use for Invigorate and other reaction abilities it gains from being a black blade.</p>"
    },
